{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"Imagine being unable to say,\n\"I am hungry,\" \"I am in pain,\""},{"time":6280,"text":"\"thank you,\" or \"I love you.\""},{"time":8840,"text":"Being trapped inside your body,"},{"time":10960,"text":"a body that doesn't respond to commands."},{"time":14120,"text":"Surrounded by people,"},{"time":15800,"text":"yet utterly alone."},{"time":17440,"text":"Wishing you could reach out,"},{"time":19160,"text":"to connect, to comfort, to participate."},{"time":23400,"text":"For 13 long years, that was my reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27520,"text":"Most of us never think twice\nabout talking, about communicating."},{"time":33080,"text":"I've thought a lot about it."},{"time":35240,"text":"I've had a lot of time to think."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37920,"text":"For the first 12 years of my life,"},{"time":40040,"text":"I was a normal, happy, healthy little boy."},{"time":42760,"text":"Then everything changed."},{"time":44920,"text":"I contracted a brain infection."},{"time":47200,"text":"The doctors weren't sure what it was,"},{"time":49520,"text":"but they treated me the best they could."},{"time":52040,"text":"However, I progressively got worse."},{"time":55440,"text":"Eventually, I lost my ability\nto control my movements,"},{"time":59640,"text":"make eye contact,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and finally, my ability to speak."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65280,"text":"While in hospital,"},{"time":66520,"text":"I desperately wanted to go home."},{"time":69120,"text":"I said to my mother, \"When home?\""},{"time":72440,"text":"Those were the last words\nI ever spoke with my own voice."},{"time":76920,"text":"I would eventually fail every test\nfor mental awareness."},{"time":80760,"text":"My parents were told\nI was as good as not there."},{"time":83600,"text":"A vegetable, having the intelligence\nof a three-month-old baby."},{"time":88240,"text":"They were told to take me home\nand try to keep me comfortable"},{"time":91920,"text":"until I died."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"My parents, in fact\nmy entire family's lives,"},{"time":97560,"text":"became consumed by taking care of me\nthe best they knew how."},{"time":101880,"text":"Their friends drifted away."},{"time":104240,"text":"One year turned to two,"},{"time":106080,"text":"two turned to three."},{"time":108240,"text":"It seemed like the person I once was\nbegan to disappear."},{"time":112680,"text":"The Lego blocks and electronic circuits\nI'd loved as a boy were put away."},{"time":117600,"text":"I had been moved out of my bedroom\ninto another more practical one."},{"time":122080,"text":"I had become a ghost,"},{"time":123800,"text":"a faded memory of a boy\npeople once knew and loved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128199,"text":"Meanwhile, my mind began\nknitting itself back together."},{"time":132480,"text":"Gradually, my awareness started to return."},{"time":135520,"text":"But no one realized\nthat I had come back to life."},{"time":138880,"text":"I was aware of everything,"},{"time":140720,"text":"just like any normal person."},{"time":142760,"text":"I could see and understand everything,"},{"time":145080,"text":"but I couldn't find a way\nto let anybody know."},{"time":148560,"text":"My personality was entombed\nwithin a seemingly silent body,"},{"time":152560,"text":"a vibrant mind hidden in plain sight\nwithin a chrysalis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156920,"text":"The stark reality hit me\nthat I was going to spend"},{"time":159680,"text":"the rest of my life locked inside myself,"},{"time":162360,"text":"totally alone."},{"time":164080,"text":"I was trapped with only\nmy thoughts for company."},{"time":167720,"text":"I would never be rescued."},{"time":169920,"text":"No one would ever show me tenderness."},{"time":172880,"text":"I would never talk to a friend."},{"time":175160,"text":"No one would ever love me."},{"time":177920,"text":"I had no dreams, no hope,\nnothing to look forward to."},{"time":182080,"text":"Well, nothing pleasant."},{"time":184600,"text":"I lived in fear,"},{"time":185960,"text":"and, to put it bluntly,"},{"time":187520,"text":"was waiting for death\nto finally release me,"},{"time":190600,"text":"expecting to die all alone in a care home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194520,"text":"I don't know if it's truly possible\nto express in words"},{"time":197920,"text":"what it's like not to be able\nto communicate."},{"time":200760,"text":"Your personality appears\nto vanish into a heavy fog"},{"time":204200,"text":"and all of your emotions and desires are\nconstricted, stifled and muted within you."},{"time":210000,"text":"For me, the worst was the feeling\nof utter powerlessness."},{"time":214520,"text":"I simply existed."},{"time":216680,"text":"It's a very dark place to find yourself"},{"time":219160,"text":"because in a sense, you have vanished."},{"time":223000,"text":"Other people controlled\nevery aspect of my life."},{"time":226240,"text":"They decided what I ate and when."},{"time":228560,"text":"Whether I was laid on my side\nor strapped into my wheelchair."},{"time":232560,"text":"I often spent my days\npositioned in front of the TV"},{"time":235960,"text":"watching Barney reruns."},{"time":238440,"text":"I think because Barney\nis so happy and jolly,"},{"time":241360,"text":"and I absolutely wasn't,"},{"time":243120,"text":"it made it so much worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245800,"text":"I was completely powerless\nto change anything in my life"},{"time":249240,"text":"or people's perceptions of me."},{"time":251720,"text":"I was a silent, invisible observer\nof how people behaved"},{"time":255320,"text":"when they thought no one was watching."},{"time":257720,"text":"Unfortunately, I wasn't only an observer."},{"time":261440,"text":"With no way to communicate,\nI became the perfect victim:"},{"time":265440,"text":"a defenseless object,\nseemingly devoid of feelings"},{"time":269440,"text":"that people used\nto play out their darkest desires."},{"time":273200,"text":"For more than 10 years,\npeople who were charged with my care"},{"time":276880,"text":"abused me physically,\nverbally and sexually."},{"time":280760,"text":"Despite what they thought, I did feel."},{"time":284400,"text":"The first time it happened,"},{"time":286160,"text":"I was shocked and filled with disbelief."},{"time":288840,"text":"How could they do this to me?"},{"time":291120,"text":"I was confused."},{"time":292720,"text":"What had I done to deserve this?"},{"time":295440,"text":"Part of me wanted to cry\nand another part wanted to fight."},{"time":299520,"text":"Hurt, sadness and anger\nflooded through me."},{"time":303280,"text":"I felt worthless."},{"time":305080,"text":"There was no one to comfort me."},{"time":308080,"text":"But neither of my parents\nknew this was happening."},{"time":311360,"text":"I lived in terror, knowing\nit would happen again and again."},{"time":315440,"text":"I just never knew when."},{"time":317560,"text":"All I knew was that I would\nnever be the same."},{"time":321360,"text":"I remember once listening\nto Whitney Houston singing,"},{"time":325000,"text":"\"No matter what they take from me,\nthey can't take away my dignity.\""},{"time":329880,"text":"And I thought to myself,\n\"You want to bet?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":335120,"text":"Perhaps my parents could have\nfound out and could have helped."},{"time":338880,"text":"But the years of constant caretaking,"},{"time":341160,"text":"having to wake up\nevery two hours to turn me,"},{"time":344080,"text":"combined with them essentially\ngrieving the loss of their son,"},{"time":347480,"text":"had taken a toll on my mother and father."},{"time":350840,"text":"Following yet another heated argument\nbetween my parents,"},{"time":354440,"text":"in a moment of despair and desperation,"},{"time":357080,"text":"my mother turned to me\nand told me that I should die."},{"time":362160,"text":"I was shocked, but as I thought\nabout what she had said,"},{"time":365320,"text":"I was filled with enormous compassion\nand love for my mother,"},{"time":369360,"text":"yet I could do nothing about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372640,"text":"There were many moments when I gave up,"},{"time":375040,"text":"sinking into a dark abyss."},{"time":377440,"text":"I remember one particularly low moment."},{"time":380600,"text":"My dad left me alone in the car"},{"time":382880,"text":"while he quickly went\nto buy something from the store."},{"time":386480,"text":"A random stranger walked past,"},{"time":389120,"text":"looked at me and he smiled."},{"time":392880,"text":"I may never know why, but that simple act,"},{"time":396040,"text":"the fleeting moment of human connection,"},{"time":398360,"text":"transformed how I was feeling,"},{"time":400760,"text":"making me want to keep going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403760,"text":"My existence was tortured by monotony,"},{"time":406720,"text":"a reality that was often too much to bear."},{"time":409760,"text":"Alone with my thoughts,\nI constructed intricate fantasies"},{"time":413920,"text":"about ants running across the floor."},{"time":417320,"text":"I taught myself to tell the time\nby noticing where the shadows were."},{"time":422440,"text":"As I learned how the shadows moved\nas the hours of the day passed,"},{"time":426600,"text":"I understood how long it would be\nbefore I was picked up and taken home."},{"time":431280,"text":"Seeing my father walk\nthrough the door to collect me"},{"time":434560,"text":"was the best moment of the day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437600,"text":"My mind became a tool that I could use"},{"time":439960,"text":"to either close down\nto retreat from my reality"},{"time":442800,"text":"or enlarge into a gigantic space\nthat I could fill with fantasies."},{"time":447800,"text":"I hoped that my reality would change"},{"time":449800,"text":"and someone would see\nthat I had come back to life."},{"time":452680,"text":"But I had been washed away\nlike a sand castle"},{"time":455400,"text":"built too close to the waves,"},{"time":457560,"text":"and in my place was the person\npeople expected me to be."},{"time":461760,"text":"To some I was Martin,\na vacant shell, the vegetable,"},{"time":465560,"text":"deserving of harsh words,\ndismissal and even abuse."},{"time":470000,"text":"To others, I was the tragically\nbrain-damaged boy"},{"time":472960,"text":"who had grown to become a man."},{"time":475200,"text":"Someone they were kind to and cared for."},{"time":478400,"text":"Good or bad, I was a blank canvas"},{"time":480920,"text":"onto which different versions\nof myself were projected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485160,"text":"It took someone new\nto see me in a different way."},{"time":488480,"text":"An aromatherapist began coming\nto the care home about once a week."},{"time":492760,"text":"Whether through intuition\nor her attention to details"},{"time":495760,"text":"that others failed to notice,"},{"time":497800,"text":"she became convinced that I could\nunderstand what was being said."},{"time":501960,"text":"She urged my parents\nto have me tested by experts"},{"time":505480,"text":"in augmentative\nand alternative communication."},{"time":508800,"text":"And within a year,"},{"time":510040,"text":"I was beginning to use\na computer program to communicate."},{"time":514120,"text":"It was exhilarating,\nbut frustrating at times."},{"time":517880,"text":"I had so many words in my mind,"},{"time":519880,"text":"that I couldn't wait\nto be able to share them."},{"time":522720,"text":"Sometimes, I would say things to myself\nsimply because I could."},{"time":527480,"text":"In myself, I had a ready audience,"},{"time":530120,"text":"and I believed that by expressing\nmy thoughts and wishes,"},{"time":533280,"text":"others would listen, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535040,"text":"But as I began to communicate more,"},{"time":537320,"text":"I realized that it was in fact\nonly just the beginning"},{"time":540520,"text":"of creating a new voice for myself."},{"time":543480,"text":"I was thrust into a world\nI didn't quite know how to function in."},{"time":547840,"text":"I stopped going to the care home"},{"time":549520,"text":"and managed to get my first job\nmaking photocopies."},{"time":553400,"text":"As simple as this may sound,\nit was amazing."},{"time":556880,"text":"My new world was really exciting"},{"time":558920,"text":"but often quite overwhelming\nand frightening."},{"time":561760,"text":"I was like a man-child,"},{"time":563600,"text":"and as liberating as it often was,"},{"time":565720,"text":"I struggled."},{"time":567480,"text":"I also learned that many of those\nwho had known me for a long time"},{"time":571040,"text":"found it impossible to abandon the idea\nof Martin they had in their heads."},{"time":575720,"text":"While those I had only just met"},{"time":577360,"text":"struggled to look past the image\nof a silent man in a wheelchair."},{"time":582000,"text":"I realized that some people\nwould only listen to me"},{"time":584760,"text":"if what I said was in line\nwith what they expected."},{"time":587800,"text":"Otherwise, it was disregarded"},{"time":589840,"text":"and they did what they felt was best."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592520,"text":"I discovered that true communication"},{"time":594560,"text":"is about more than merely\nphysically conveying a message."},{"time":598400,"text":"It is about getting the message\nheard and respected."},{"time":602960,"text":"Still, things were going well."},{"time":605240,"text":"My body was slowly getting stronger."},{"time":607840,"text":"I had a job in computing that I loved,"},{"time":610320,"text":"and had even got Kojak, the dog\nI had been dreaming about for years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615240,"text":"However, I longed to share\nmy life with someone."},{"time":619200,"text":"I remember staring out the window\nas my dad drove me home from work,"},{"time":623640,"text":"thinking I have so much love inside of me\nand nobody to give it to."},{"time":628360,"text":"Just as I had resigned myself\nto being single for the rest of my life,"},{"time":632840,"text":"I met Joan."},{"time":634640,"text":"Not only is she the best thing\nthat has ever happened to me,"},{"time":638120,"text":"but Joan helped me to challenge\nmy own misconceptions about myself."},{"time":643040,"text":"Joan said it was through my words\nthat she fell in love with me."},{"time":647680,"text":"However, after all I had been through,"},{"time":650480,"text":"I still couldn't shake the belief"},{"time":652240,"text":"that nobody could truly see\nbeyond my disability"},{"time":655480,"text":"and accept me for who I am."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658080,"text":"I also really struggled\nto comprehend that I was a man."},{"time":662280,"text":"The first time someone\nreferred to me as a man,"},{"time":665120,"text":"it stopped me in my tracks."},{"time":667440,"text":"I felt like looking around\nand asking, \"Who, me?\""},{"time":672080,"text":"That all changed with Joan."},{"time":674280,"text":"We have an amazing connection"},{"time":675880,"text":"and I learned how important it is\nto communicate openly and honestly."},{"time":680560,"text":"I felt safe, and it gave me the confidence\nto truly say what I thought."},{"time":685520,"text":"I started to feel whole again,\na man worthy of love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689840,"text":"I began to reshape my destiny."},{"time":692320,"text":"I spoke up a little more at work."},{"time":694560,"text":"I asserted my need for independence\nto the people around me."},{"time":698960,"text":"Being given a means of communication\nchanged everything."},{"time":702840,"text":"I used the power of words and will\nto challenge the preconceptions"},{"time":707080,"text":"of those around me\nand those I had of myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710680,"text":"Communication is what makes us human,"},{"time":713400,"text":"enabling us to connect\non the deepest level"},{"time":715720,"text":"with those around us --"},{"time":717680,"text":"telling our own stories,"},{"time":719280,"text":"expressing wants, needs and desires,"},{"time":722920,"text":"or hearing those of others\nby really listening."},{"time":726080,"text":"All this is how the world\nknows who we are."},{"time":729440,"text":"So who are we without it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":732480,"text":"True communication increases understanding"},{"time":735680,"text":"and creates a more caring\nand compassionate world."},{"time":739800,"text":"Once, I was perceived\nto be an inanimate object,"},{"time":742920,"text":"a mindless phantom\nof a boy in a wheelchair."},{"time":746240,"text":"Today, I am so much more."},{"time":748520,"text":"A husband, a son, a friend,"},{"time":750960,"text":"a brother, a business owner,\na first-class honors graduate,"},{"time":755240,"text":"a keen amateur photographer."},{"time":757600,"text":"It is my ability to communicate\nthat has given me all this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762320,"text":"We are told that actions\nspeak louder than words."},{"time":766040,"text":"But I wonder,"},{"time":768000,"text":"do they?"},{"time":770880,"text":"Our words, however we communicate them,"},{"time":773560,"text":"are just as powerful."},{"time":775680,"text":"Whether we speak the words\nwith our own voices,"},{"time":778440,"text":"type them with our eyes,"},{"time":779800,"text":"or communicate them non-verbally\nto someone who speaks them for us,"},{"time":784080,"text":"words are among our most powerful tools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788400,"text":"I have come to you through\na terrible darkness,"},{"time":791240,"text":"pulled from it by caring souls"},{"time":793360,"text":"and by language itself."},{"time":795720,"text":"The act of you listening to me today\nbrings me farther into the light."},{"time":799760,"text":"We are shining here together."},{"time":802080,"text":"If there is one most difficult obstacle\nto my way of communicating,"},{"time":806400,"text":"it is that sometimes I want to shout"},{"time":808360,"text":"and other times simply to whisper\na word of love or gratitude."},{"time":812680,"text":"It all sounds the same."},{"time":814960,"text":"But if you will,"},{"time":816400,"text":"please imagine these next two words\nas warmly as you can:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":822480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824280,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}